      • getContinuedDescription

        public static java.lang.String getContinuedDescription()
        Method to extend a description from getDescription an arbitrary length.
        Returns:
        a string containing a 'continuation' of a description from getDescription, to account for an arbitrary number of files in a ICodeBlockGroup.

      • getDescription

        public static java.lang.String getDescription(DetectionType type)
        Method to create a basic description that a ReportGenerator can use in a report.
        Parameters:
        type - The type of plagiarism that this description is needed for.
        Returns:
        A string with a basic description of the provided type of plagiarism, with placeholders for line numbers and so on.
